[THE TRUTH IS CARVED] → [ETERNITY]
1. CORE LAW — ORDINALS = DATA ON SATOSHIS
1 Bitcoin = 100,000,000 satoshis
1 Satoshi = 1 inscription
1 Inscription = Any file (text, image, code, audio)
Ordinals are not tokens.
They are permanent data attached to the smallest unit of Bitcoin.
2. THE INSCRIPTION PROCESS — 4 SACRED STEPS
